      ],
      "plan": [
        "Open `crates/ralph/src/productivity/calculations.rs` and locate the `best_day` aggregation loop.",
        "Refactor the conditional update to avoid `unwrap()` even behind guards (`map_or` / `match`).",
        "Run productivity/unit tests touching calculations."
      ],
      "notes": [
        "Refactored best_day update to use Option::is_none_or (no unwrap after is_none guard).",
        "Clippy: prefer is_none_or over map_or(true, ...) per unnecessary_map_or.",
        "Validated: cargo test -p ralph-agent-loop productivity; make agent-ci passed."
      ],
      "request": "Refactor `best_day` updates in `crates/ralph/src/productivity/calculations.rs` to remove `best_day.as_ref().unwrap()` after `is_none()` guards—use `match`, `if let`, or `map_or` for equivalent behavior and clearer control flow. Run productivity/calculation tests. Scope: this task only—no new queue items.",
