      "request": "Validate `WebhookConfig.url` usage end-to-end (`contracts/config/webhook.rs` through `webhook/worker/delivery.rs`). Add URL safety: default HTTPS-only, optional opt-in for http, and reject or clearly warn on loopback, link-local, and metadata-style hosts unless explicitly allowed. Update schema/tests as needed. Run `cargo test -p ralph`. Scope: this task only—no new queue items.",
