      ],
      "plan": [
        "Inspect current `retry_delay` and call graph in `delivery.rs` (scheduled retry path uses `retry_delay(task.msg.config.retry_backoff, retry_number)`).",
        "Implement exponential+jitter+cap with deterministic unit tests for backoff sequence bounds.",
        "Validate behavior under configured retry limits and document any config surface changes if required.",
        "Run webhook delivery tests."
      ],
      "notes": [
        "Webhook retry delay now uses exponential backoff with bounded jitter and a 30s cap.",
        "Added deterministic retry-delay tests for exponential growth, jitter bounds, cap, and overflow.",
        "Updated webhook retry docs and verified targeted webhook tests plus make agent-ci."
      ],
      "request": "Replace linear `retry_delay` in `crates/ralph/src/webhook/worker/delivery.rs` with exponential backoff, jitter, and a maximum cap; keep existing timeout and redaction behavior. Add tests for bounded delay sequences. Run webhook delivery tests. Scope: this task only—no new queue items.",
