      ],
      "plan": [
        "Inventory all `.expect(` sites in `webhook/worker/runtime.rs` (worker spawn, scheduler spawn, startup barrier, dispatcher cache).",
        "Read audit Quick win #3 if available.",
        "Refactor spawn paths to propagate errors and choose a documented fallback path.",
        "Add regression tests simulating failure where feasible (or unit-test the decision helper).",
        "Run targeted webhook/runtime tests."
      ],
      "notes": [
        "Made webhook dispatcher startup fallible and disabled webhooks for the run on startup failure instead of panicking.",
        "Updated enqueue path to drop webhook events with diagnostics when dispatcher initialization is unavailable.",
        "Added runtime regression tests for thread-spawn failure and startup-handshake timeout.",
        "Verified with targeted webhook tests and make ci."
      ],
      "request": "In `crates/ralph/src/webhook/worker/runtime.rs`, replace `.expect()` on worker/scheduler spawn, startup handshake, and dispatcher init with `Result` propagation and a defined fallback: degrade to sync delivery or disable webhooks for the run with a clear operator-visible warning—no process abort on thread spawn failure. Add regression coverage where practical. Run webhook/runtime tests. Scope: this task only—no new queue items.",
